{"thag6.6:0.1":"Theragatha 6.6 ","thag6.6:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.6:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.6:0.4":"Sappadasattheragatha ","thag6.6:1.1":"“Pannavisativassani, ","thag6.6:1.2":"yato pabbajito aham; ","thag6.6:1.3":"Accharasanghatamattampi, ","thag6.6:1.4":"cetosantimanajjhagam. ","thag6.6:2.1":"Aladdha cittassekaggam, ","thag6.6:2.2":"kamaragena attito; ","thag6.6:2.3":"Baha paggayha kandanto, ","thag6.6:2.4":"vihara upanikkhamim. ","thag6.6:3.1":"Sattham va aharissami, ","thag6.6:3.2":"Ko attho jivitena me; ","thag6.6:3.3":"Katham hi sikkham paccakkham, ","thag6.6:3.4":"Kalam kubbetha madiso. ","thag6.6:4.1":"Tadaham khuramadaya, ","thag6.6:4.2":"mancakamhi upavisim; ","thag6.6:4.3":"Parinito khuro asi, ","thag6.6:4.4":"dhamanim chettumattano. ","thag6.6:5.1":"Tato me manasikaro, ","thag6.6:5.2":"yoniso udapajjatha; ","thag6.6:5.3":"Adinavo paturahu, ","thag6.6:5.4":"nibbida samatitthatha. ","thag6.6:6.1":"Tato cittam vimucci me, ","thag6.6:6.2":"passa dhammasudhammatam; ","thag6.6:6.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag6.6:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanan”ti. ","thag6.6:6.5":"… Sappadaso thero …. "}